(159, 'Tom Ford Private Blend Oud Wood Candle', 'TOM FORD', 999000, 71, '&nbsp;', 'mp;nbsp; Oud wood is one of the most rare, precious and expensive ingredients in a perfumer&amp;amp;#39;s arsenal. Exotic rose wood and cardamom give way to a smoky blend of rare oud wood, sandalwood and vetiver. Tonka bean and amber add warmth and sensuality.Immerse yourself in the world of Tom Ford with artfully crafted Private Blend Candles designed to scent and style your home.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/OUDWOODCANDLE_600x600.jpg?v=1611035428'),
