(161, 'Tom Ford Private Blend Neroli Portofino Candle', 'TOM FORD', 999000, 2, '&nbsp;', 'mp;nbsp; Notes:Tunisian Neroli, Italian Bergamot, Sicilian Lemon, Winter Yellow Mandarin, Orange Flower, Lavender.Style:Vibrant. Sparkling. Transportive. To Tom Ford, this scent perfectly captures the cool breezes, sparkling clear water, and lush foliage of the Italian Rivera. His reinvention of a classic eau de cologne features crisp citrus oils, surprising floral notes, and amber undertones to leave a splashy yet substantive impression.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NEROLIPORTOFINOCANDLE_600x600.jpg?v=1611035839'),
(162, 'La Vie Est Belle L&rsquo;EAU DE PARFUM LIMITED EDITION', 'LANCOME', 569000, 14, '75ml Eau de Parfum TESTER BOX', ' La Vie Est Belle Edition Limitee by Lancome is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. La Vie Est Belle Edition Limitee was launched in 2016. La Vie Est Belle Edition Limitee was created by Olivier Polge, Dominique Ropion and Anne Flipo. Top notes are Black Currant, Orange and Pear; middle notes are Jasmine, iris and Orange Blossom; base notes are Praline, Vanilla, Patchouli, Tonka Bean and Bitter Almond.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/image_8b700cbf-c217-4d43-b57e-456cde030cfd_600x600.jpg?v=1611157357'),
(163, 'GUCCI MEMOIRE D\'UNE ODEUR PINK', 'GUCCI', 579000, 5, '&lt;span&gt;100ml Eau de Parfum&lt;/span&gt;', 'eacute;moire d&amp;rsquo;une Odeur&amp;rsquo;s Roman chamomile is structured with Indian Coral Jasmine petals, has a depth of precious musks, and wood notes of sandalwood, cedarwood, as well as a vanilla. The fragrance aims to disrupt the traditional olfactive families that classifies fragrances, with a new modern fragrance category, Mineral.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/Gucci-Memoire-D-UNE-ODEUR-100ml-Pink-600x600_600x600.png?v=1615006829'),
(164, 'Jewellessence Blue by Designer SHAIK, Opulent Shaik Classic No. 77 (TESTER BOX)', 'DESIGNER SHAIK', 999000, 35, '100ml Eau de Parfum (TESTER BOX)', ' Opulent Shaik Classic No 77Opulent Shaik Classic No 77 by Shaik is a Oriental fragrance for men. Top notes are bergamot, lemon, lavender and basil; middle notes are geranium, cloves, apple and cinnamon; base notes are cedar, patchouli, oakmoss, labdanum, vanilla and musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/PODSOpulentShaikhMNo.77btl_600x600.jpg?v=1611475833'),
(165, 'Tom Ford Black Orchid 30ML', 'TOM FORD', 399000, 37, 'Eau De Parfum Spray 30ml', ' Black Orchid by Tom Ford is an oriental floral fragrance for women. Black Orchid contains a luxurious mix of floral, citrus and wood notes, with chocolate, tuberose, patchouli, orchid and vanilla being the most noticeable. This dark, mysterious and sophisticated scent has become one of Tom Ford&amp;rsquo;s most beloved releases. Black Orchid by Tom Ford was launched in 2006.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BLACKORSHID_600x600.jpg?v=1611477045'),
(166, 'WATERLILY 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 63, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Radiant white waterlilies, crown jewels of a secret garden pond. Discovered on our adventures. These pristine petals release a clean floralcy that stirs and enchants. The dewy freshness of these floating blooms is enhanced with a flourish of jasmine sambac and neroli.&amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMWATERLILY30ML_600x600.png?v=1611478820'),
(167, 'OSMANTHUS 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 10, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Delicately exotic, these tiny white blossoms capture the duality of soft, apricot sweetness against contrasting deep, warming notes. Luminous petitgrain and luscious peach and orange flower ripple over voluptuous cashmere wood.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMOSMANTHUS30ML_600x600.png?v=1611479241'),
(168, 'YUJA 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 99, 'Cologne 30ML&nbsp;', 'mp;nbsp; Inspired by the spirited streets of Seoul, the&amp;nbsp;Jo Malone London Yuja Cologne&amp;nbsp;balances exotic notes of thirst-quenching fruitiness against the&amp;nbsp;arresting essence&amp;nbsp;of deep woody accords, culminating in a fresh, fierce and truly tantalising aroma. Plush gardens roll out across an open stretch of land, replete with the sharp, sweet scent of sparkling Yuja. The bright, zesty aroma shines at the top of the cologne before slipping into a fragrant heart of Clary Sage. Cool, calming and confident in equal measure, this core note drifts from the centre to enhance the Jo Malone perfume with an earthy, herbaceous quality.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/c6a52738-4de7-477c-9ad5-1a8942531638_600x600.jpg?v=1611479560'),
(169, 'SILK BLOSSOM 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 57, 'Cologone 30ML', ' Forever finding new ways to captivate our senses, Jo Malone London continues to tempt us with Blossoms - a collection of fragrances that capture the refreshing natural scents of springtime blooms. Enter: Silk Blossom. A sweet and enticing scent, the cologne is a celebration of the flowers that are irresistible to hummingbirds and butterflies. Apricot fresh with a touch of spice, it&amp;amp;#39;s enhanced with soft heliotrope, and deepened with earthy moss. Jo Malone London cologne Scent: Silk Blossom Top note: white pepper.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMSILKBLOSSOM30ML_600x600.png?v=1611480008'),
(170, 'CADE &amp; CEDARWOOD 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 62, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Jo Malone London&amp;amp;#39;s cologne recreates the scent of smoldering embers in a wood-burning stove and the feeling of &amp;amp;quot;basking in its warm and comforting glow.&amp;amp;quot; It&amp;amp;#39;s infused with notes of smoky Cade and deep Cedarwood, complemented with an accord of Ciste Labdanum and sweet Vanilla. This 30ml bottle is perfect for slipping into your tote, so you can keep your scent topped up all day.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/3f72ec83-8d32-4e32-82ef-4762df88b18a_600x600.jpg?v=1611481115'),
(171, 'WILLOW &amp; AMBER 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 2, 'Cologne 30ML', ' The expressive weeping willow, gently draping across the fresh morning water. Captured in the woody pairing of cashmere wood and smoky vetiver, enhanced by softly sensual amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMWILLOW_AMBER_600x600.jpg?v=1611481303'),
(172, 'NETTLE &amp; WILD ACHIELLA by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 82, 'Cologne 30ML&nbsp;', 'mp;nbsp; The fresh green fragrance of Jo Malone London&amp;rsquo;s Nettle &amp;amp;amp;amp; Wild Achillea Cologne begins by unveiling the floral softness and delicate petally touch of white yarrow. At its heart, a green stingy note peeks through with a peppery top, while the vetiver base softens the scent with a lingering trail of white musk. Its decorative bottle comes presented with hand-painted floral illustrations.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JLNETTLE_WILDACHIELLA_600x600.jpg?v=1611481813'),
(173, 'LUPIN &amp; PATCHOULI by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 83, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Lupin &amp;amp;amp;amp; Patchouli by Jo Malone London is a Chypre Floral fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Lupin &amp;amp;amp;amp; Patchouli was launched in 2019. Lupin &amp;amp;amp;amp; Patchouli was created by Yann Vasnier and Louise Turner.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMLUPINPATCHOULI_600x600.jpg?v=1611481984'),
(174, 'CHANEL NO. 5 L\'EAU 35ML', 'CHANEL', 399000, 12, 'Eau de Toilette 35ML', ' Chanel No. 5 L&amp;amp;#39;eau Perfume by Chanel, Designed by master perfumer Olivier Polge, Chanel No. 5 L&amp;amp;#39;eau is intended to bring all the sophistication and class of Chanel No. 5 to the younger generations. This lighter, fresher version draws the nose in with fresh opening notes of lemon, mandarin orange, neroli, bergamot, lime, and aldehydes. Middle notes are ylang ylang, jasmine, and may rose. The base notes for this fragrance are rich musk, vanilla, cedar, and orris root to keep with the timeless classic without sacrificing the simplicity of the scent.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NO5WHITE35ML_600x600.jpg?v=1611490031'),
(175, 'CHANEL NO. 5 EAU DE PARFUM 35ML', 'CHANEL', 0, 69, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'nce of femininity. An aldehyde floral bouquet housed in an iconic bottle with a minimalist design. A timeless, legendary fragrance. Olfactory atmosphere The eau de parfum draws inspiration from the parfum with which it shares its floral aldehyde signature. This floral bouquet composed around May Rose and Jasmine features bright citrus top notes. Aldehydes create a unique presence, and the smooth touch of Vanilla an incredibly sensual trail.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NO535ML_600x600.jpg?v=1611490314'),
(176, 'CREED SILVER MOUNTAIN WATER', 'CREED', 999000, 5, 'Eau de Parfum 100ML', ' Inspired by the exhilarating crispness of mountain air and the purity of cascading alpine streams, a bracing landscape in which the Creed family find relaxation and renewal.&amp;nbsp; A contempory scent which captures the purity of citrus notes, tea, blackcurrant and musk.Cool, clean, icy and mentholated -reminiscent of sparkling streams coursing through the snowcapped Swiss Alps.Top notes:&amp;nbsp;Bergamot, Mandarin, NeroliHeart notes:&amp;nbsp;Green Tea, Blackcurrant BudBase notes:&amp;nbsp;Sandalwood, Musk', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/CREEDSILVERMONTAIN_600x600.jpg?v=1611491714'),
(177, 'Gucci The Alchemist\'s Garden: A Chant for The Nymph', 'GUCCI', 1090000, 1, 'Eau de Parfum 100ML', ' Crafted from pure natural plants and flowers layered with modern molecules, each fragrance and formula in the Alchemist&amp;rsquo;s Garden is inspired by the science of alchemy, telling the story of a place, a moment, or a memory. A Chant for the Nymph is an ode to tropical forests filled with sublimating solar flowers. The fragrance is inspired by the Frangipani, which symbolizes immortality for the heavenly and enduring smell that it releases on warm nights. Hiding behind the intoxicating Ylang Ylang and sensual Tiare flower, the flowers are warmed by soft Vanilla.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GUCCICHANTFORTHENYMPH_600x600.jpg?v=1611492189');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `price`, `stock`, `type`, `description`, `image_source`) VALUES
(178, 'NEROLI PORTOFINO 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 70, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' About Neroli Portofino Part of Tom Ford&amp;amp;#39;s Private Blend Collection Neroli Portofino fragrance notes Top Notes Tunisian neroli, Italian bergamot, Sicilian lemon, Mandarin, Lavender, Myrtle, Rosemary, Bitter orange Heart Notes African orange blossom, Jasmine, Neroli, Pitosporum Base notes Amber, Ambrette seed, Angelica', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TFNEROLIPORTOFINO100ML_600x600.jpg?v=1611493751'),
(179, 'NOIR DE NOIR 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 2, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' Noir de Noir by Tom Ford is a Chypre fragrance for women and men. Noir de Noir was launched in 2007. Noir de Noir was created by Jacques Cavallier and Harry Fremont. Top note is Saffron; middle notes are Black Rose, Truffle and Floral Notes; base notes are Patchouli, Vanilla, Agarwood (Oud) and Oakmoss.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TFNOIR100ML_600x600.jpg?v=1611493957'),
(180, 'ROSE PRICK 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 79, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' Rose Prick by Tom Ford is a Chypre Floral fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Rose Prick was launched in 2020. Top notes are Sichuan Pepper and Turmeric; middle notes are May Rose, Bulgarian Rose and Turkish Rose; base notes are Patchouli and Tonka Bean.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/4a0d8ea4-b99b-4d44-b865-1a9ddf8e292f_600x600.jpg?v=1611495569'),
(181, 'CAFE ROSE 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 1, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' The oriental floral perfume Tom Ford Cafe Rose was created in 2012 for men and women. The basis of the Cafe Rose perfume composition is a bouquet of roses, complemented by a deep tonic coffee aroma. Tom Ford Cafe Rose is characterized by a delicious, exotic, seductive aroma. The Cafe Rose fragrance invites us to dive into the secret process of growing rare varieties of roses. This composition consists of three different types of rose essence, flavored with spices and dark coffee. Top notes:&amp;nbsp;Saffron, Black pepper, May rose; Heart notes:&amp;nbsp;Turkish rose, Bulgarian rose, coffee; Base notes:&amp;nbsp;Frankincense, Ambergris, Sandalwood, Patchouli.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TFCAFEROSE1OOML_600x600.jpg?v=1611497198'),
(182, 'SOLEIL BLANC 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 81, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', ' Ford is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women and men. Eau de Soleil Blanc was launched in 2018. Top notes are Bitter Orange, Neroli, Pistachio, Bergamot, Citron, Petitgrain, Cardamom, Pink Pepper and Caraway; middle notes are Tuberose, Tunisian Orange Blossom, Ylang-Ylang, Jasmine and Galbanum; base notes are Coconut, Vanilla, Tonka Bean, Amber and Benzoin.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLSOLEILBLANC_600x600.jpg?v=1611497568'),
(183, 'NOIR DE NOIR 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 20, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 's a Chypre fragrance for women and men. Noir de Noir was launched in 2007. Noir de Noir was created by Jacques Cavallier and Harry Fremont. Top note is Saffron; middle notes are Black Rose, Truffle and Floral Notes; base notes are Patchouli, Vanilla, Agarwood (Oud) and Oakmoss.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLNOIRDENOIR_600x600.jpg?v=1611498098'),
(184, 'JASMINE ROUGE 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 81, 'Eau de Parfum 50ML', ' Tom Ford Jasmin Rouge Perfume by Tom Ford, Tom Ford Jasmin Rouge is a fragrance that was introduced in 2011 along with Violet Blonde, and Santal&amp;nbsp;Blush. The fragrance opens with notes of bergamot, mandarin, cinnamon, ginger, cardamom, black and white pepper. At its heart, the scent contains jasmine, neroli, ylang-ylang, and clary sage. The base notes are Mexican vanilla, labdanum, leather, wood, and amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLJASMINEROUGE_600x600.jpg?v=1611498370'),
(185, 'TOM FORD Tobacco Oud 50ML', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 15, 'Eau de Parfum 50ML', ' Tobacco Oud by Tom Ford is a Woody Spicy fragrance for women and men. Tobacco Oud was launched in 2013. The nose behind this fragrance is Olivier Gillotin. Top note is Whiskey; middle notes are Spicy Notes, Cinnamon and Coriander; base notes are Tobacco, Agarwood (Oud), Sandalwood, Patchouli, Incense, Benzoin, Vanilla and Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLTOBACCOOUD_600x600.jpg?v=1611498749'),
(186, 'SOLE DI POSITANO 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 92, 'Eau de Parfum 50ML', ' Sole di Positano by Tom Ford is a Citrus fragrance for women and men. Sole di Positano was launched in 2017. Top notes are Bitter Orange, Mandarin Orange, Lemon, Calabrian bergamot and Petitgrain; middle notes are Neroli, Orange Blossom, Jasmine, Shiso, Ylang-Ylang and Lily-of-the-Valley; base note is Moss.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLSOLEDIPOTISANO_600x600.jpg?v=1611499268'),
(187, 'TOBACCO VANILLE 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 0, 45, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'agrance that highlights a heady modern fusion between sweet, sensual vanilla and spicy tobacco accord. With a rich scent that paints the marvel of an English Gentleman&amp;amp;#39;s club, this fragrance opens into a medley of tobacco and spicy notes. The heart samples a deep vanilla chord surrounded in tonka bean, tobacco blossom and bitter cacao. Finishing the scent is a final layer of woods and dried fruits.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLTOBACCOVANILLE_600x600.jpg?v=1611499500'),
(188, 'LOST CHERRY 50ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 659000, 42, 'Eau de Parfum 50ML', ' Lost Cherry by Tom Ford is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Lost Cherry was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Louise Turner. Top notes are Sour Cherry, Bitter Almond and Liquor; middle notes are Sour Cherry, Plum, Turkish Rose and Jasmine Sambac; base notes are Tonka Bean, Vanilla, Peru Balsam, Benzoin, Cinnamon, Sandalwood, Cedar, Cloves, Vetiver and Patchouli.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/50MLLOSTCHERRY_600x600.jpg?v=1611499721'),
(189, 'DIPTYQUE PHILOSYKOS', 'DIPTYQUE', 599000, 83, 'Eau de Parfum 75ml', ' The memory of a Greek summer at Mount Pelion where, to get to the sea, there was a natural grove of wild sun-soaked fig trees to cross through. Philosykos is an ode to the entire fig tree: the green freshness of the leaves, the milky flavour of the figs, underpinned by the woody density of the tree.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/4ecd48fd-cc07-4e6e-924f-98a91b419b9a_600x600.jpg?v=1611501551'),
(190, 'Y Eau Fraiche Yves Saint Laurent', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 599000, 96, 'Eau de Toilette&nbsp;100ml', 'sp;100ml Y Eau Fraiche by Yves Saint Laurent is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Y Eau Fraiche&amp;nbsp;was launched in 2020. Top notes are Lemon, Ginger and Pepper; middle notes are Geranium, Lavender, Mint and Juniper Berries; base notes are Cedar and Olibanum.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/YSLEAUFRAICE_600x600.jpg?v=1611501997'),
(191, 'Beau De Jour Eau de Parfum by Tom Ford', 'TOM FORD', 799000, 10, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' Beau De Jour Eau de Parfum by Tom Ford is a Aromatic Fougere fragrance for men. This is a new fragrance. Beau De Jour Eau de Parfum was launched in 2020. Top notes are Lavender Extract and Lavender; middle notes are Rosemary, Oakmoss, Mint, Basil and Geranium; base notes are Patchouli and Amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TFBEAUDEJOUR_600x600.jpg?v=1611502299'),
(192, 'LE LABO BAIE 19', 'LE LABO', 799000, 53, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' Inspired by the olfactive phenomenon of petrichor &amp;ndash; the distinctive yet elusive smell that lingers after heavy rainfall &amp;ndash; Le Labo&amp;rsquo;s Baie 19 perfume is imbued with an equally mysterious quality that reveals itself when in contact with the skin. Just like the drops of water that bring life to flora after a long drought, Baie 19 revitalises the dry juniper berry and patchouli with salty ambrox, spicy cade and woody musks.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOBAIE19_600x600.jpg?v=1611502858'),
(193, 'LE LABO GAIAC 10 TOKYO', 'LE LABO', 799000, 88, 'Eau de Parfum 100ml', ' A Tokyo-inspired perfume could smell like yakitori, smog, and underground transit, but instead Le Labo bottled up the Japanese humidity and made it tense, earthy, and woody thanks to a handful of rural notes, like cedar and frankincense. So, the next time you&amp;rsquo;re trapped in a metro tunnel, gripping the only empty inches of free pole space in sight, hoping you have hand sanitizer in your purse, sniff your wrist and transport yourself to the Japanese forest floor where the soul-crushing pain of your daily commute is nothing but a distant memory.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOGAIAC_600x600.jpg?v=1611503360'),
(194, 'Jo Malone London Peony &amp; Blush Suede Scent Surround&trade; Diffuser', 'JO MALONE', 799000, 56, 'Size 165ml', ' This sleekly designed diffuser effortlessly and continuously adds an enveloping scent to any space.The essence of charm, this scent captures exquisitely fragile peonies in voluptuous bloom. A flirtatious, juicy bite of red apple and the opulence of jasmine, rose, and gillyflower mingle with the sensuality of soft, blush suede for a luxurious and seductive trail.From colognes and candles to bath and body care, each Jo Malone London product comes presented in their signature gift box and ribbon.Place reeds into the oil, then allow 24 to 36 hours for the fragrance to diffuse for the continuous Scent Surround&amp;trade; experience. Fragrance will last for around three to four months.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/PEONYOIL_600x600.jpg?v=1611504026'),
(195, 'HONEY &amp; CROCUS 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 45, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Jo Malone Honey &amp;amp;amp;amp; Crocus is a cologne with floral and gourmet scent for women and men, created in 2018 by perfumer Mathilde Bijaoue. The natural flavour of Honey &amp;amp;amp;amp; Crocus from the brand&amp;amp;#39;s new limited edition collection, which is based on English cultural traditions and dedicated to the rich nature and soothing aromas of the UK countryside.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMHONEYCROCUS_600x600.jpg?v=1611534886'),
(196, 'POPPY &amp; BARLEY 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 27, 'Cologne 30ML', ' The new British Fields series, designed with the concept of FRAGRANCE COMBINING&amp;trade; art, contains 5 unique styles of limited-edition fragrances, each of them presents its simple and elegant style.The colorful red poppies swaying in the golden wheat field illuminated by the sun, the violet and black currant intertwined with the fruit, nestled in the embrace of barley and wheat bran, plus the romance of white musk, full of fascinating vitality, at the same time, exudes a soft and pleasant atmosphere.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMPOPPY_BARLEY_600x600.jpg?v=1611535192'),
(197, 'GREEN WHEAT &amp; MEADOWSHEET 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 9, 'Cologne 30ML', ' An English field at dawn, full of the joys of spring. Filled with young, green wheat. Crisp and fresh. Balanced with a zesty twist of grapefruit. Mingled with soft, white notes of meadowsweet. Pretty. Fresh. Powdery.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMGREENWHEAT_600x600.jpg?v=1611535403'),
(198, 'OAT &amp; CORNFLOWER 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 59, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Wholesome oats gathered from the field, fit for a hearty feast. Warm and delicious. Enlivened by vivid blue cornflowers and a hint of hazelnut. Complemented by an elegant vetiver base. Mouthwatering. Warm. Sensual.Part of the Jo Malone London English Fields Collection.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMOATCORNFLOWER_600x600.jpg?v=1611535661'),
(199, 'PRIMEROSE &amp; RYE 30ML by JO MALONE', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 58, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Rolling fields dotted with primroses. Swaying softly on a spring breeze. Warmed by golden corn. Brightened with mimosa. On an addictive base of rye and vanilla. Filled with sunshine. Vivid. Glowing. Addictive.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMPRIMEROSE_RYE_600x600.jpg?v=1611536136'),
(200, 'Amber &amp; Lavender 30ML by Jo Malone', 'JO MALONE', 349000, 71, 'Cologne 30ML', ' Known for her fashion credentials, Poppy Delevingne&amp;nbsp;redressed perfume bottles for a curated collection&amp;nbsp;dubbed &amp;amp;quot;Queen of Pop&amp;amp;#39;. Within the brightly colored vessel is the British fragrance brand&amp;amp;#39;s refined Amber &amp;amp;amp;amp; Lavender cologne; a classic scent that pulls French lavender and woody petitgrain through the warm, honey-like scent of amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JMAMBERLAVENDER_600x600.jpg?v=1611536595'),
(201, 'GUCCI GUILTY POUR FEMME', 'GUCCI', 579000, 62, 'Eau de Parfum 90ML', ' Gucci Guilty Pour Femme EDP is a wonderful perfume, for the optimistic and playful woman who appreciates her whole life with is especially grateful. The scent opens at the top with sour lime, juicy orange, and spicy pink pepper that adds a delicious and oriental touch to the whole scent. The next notes that will enchant your senses come from the large bouquet of flowers, which consists of hyacinths, violets, roses and beautiful fragrant geraniums that get your thoughts directed to the first spring day when the flowers begin to bloom in full bloom. A wonderful Eau de Parfum that is most delicately rounded off at the bottom with the scent of patchouli and amber that makes it warm and makes it envelop the body in the most guilty way. A must-have for the spacious woman with respect for herself and her surroundings.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GUCCIGUILTYPOURFEMME_600x600.jpg?v=1611536952'),
(202, 'DAVIDOFF COOL WATER WOMAN', 'DAVIDOFF', 549000, 45, 'Eau de Toilette 100ML', ' With a name that announces an aquatic blend of crisp aromas, Cool Water by Davidoff evokes images of days at the beach, with fresh water hitting the shore and bursting in cool droplets into the breezy air. Pineapple, quince and melon notes open this scent on fresh fruity tones, with lily and lotus watery hints emerging as an energizing fragrant mix. Making its debut in 1996, Cool Water eau de toilette spray for women is a clean and invigorating summer scent, the perfect choice when you need your fragrance to cool your senses down.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DAVIDOFFWOMANEDT_600x600.jpg?v=1611537285'),
(203, 'MISS DIOR ROSE N ROSES  by DIOR', 'DIOR', 0, 6, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'l eau de toilette. A profusion of fresh and colourful Grasse Rose petals, vivified by citrusy dew. For Miss Dior Rose N&amp;amp;#39;Roses, Fran&amp;ccedil;ois Demachy crafted a fresh rose with bright, vibrant florality, vivified by citrusy notes. The sensation of an armful of fresh and colourful petals that sweeps you away to an endless field of blooming roses.The heart of this new fragrance swirls with a rose grown by the exclusive partners of the house of Dior, and harvested using traditional methods to preserve its most precious properties.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIORROSE_600x600.png?v=1611537595'),
(204, 'TWILLY D\'HERMES 50ML', 'HERMES', 0, 75, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'irl, a daring fragrance woven with striking ginger and sensual tuberose. A floral, spicy and exotic eau de parfum.Olfactory emotion: Warm, SensualMain raw materials: Ginger, Tuberose, Sandalwood', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TWILLY_600x600.jpg?v=1611537887'),
