(209, 'Luna by Penhaligon\'s', 'PENHALIGON&rsquo;S', 999000, 54, 'Eau De Toilette 100ML', ' Luna by Penhaligon&amp;amp;#39;s is a fragrance for women and men. Luna was launched in 2016. Top notes are Lemon, Bergamot and Bitter Orange; middle notes are Juniper Berries, Rose and Jasmine; base notes are Balsam Fir, Musk and Ambergris.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LUNA_600x600.jpg?v=1611540565'),
(210, 'Penhaligon\'s Endymion Eau De Cologne', 'PENHALIGON&rsquo;S', 999000, 36, 'Eau De Cologne 100ml', ' Born from a time when one&amp;rsquo;s toilette or cologne was of the highest concern, Penhaligon&amp;rsquo;s create innovative fragrances that tell a story. Founded by William Penhaligon in the 1870&amp;rsquo;s, this classic British company continues to create incredible fragrances that take your senses on a journey like no other.Spicy and fresh, the Endymion Eau De Cologne is a fragrance of sensual contrasts. This distinct fragrance opens up with soft citrus tones give way to a heart of geranium and coffee absolute, finished off with a strong base of nutmeg, leather, frankincense and myrrh. Housed within a beautiful glass bottle, Endymion is perfect for the mysterious modern gentleman.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ENDYMION_600x600.jpg?v=1611540970'),
(211, 'Jo Malone Myrrh &amp; Tonka Scent Surround&trade; Diffuser', 'JO MALONE', 799000, 99, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'that effortlessly and continuously adds the enveloping scent of Myrrh &amp;amp;amp;amp; Tonka to any space. Fragrance story: Rich, hand-harvested sap of the Namibian myrrh tree mingles with the warm almond and delicious vanilla notes of tonka bean to create Myrrh &amp;amp;amp;amp; Tonka. Notes: Namibian myrrh tree, almond, vanilla, tonka bean. How to use: Place the reeds into the oil then allow 24&amp;ndash;36 hours for the fragrance to diffuse for the continuous Scent Surround experience. The fragrance will last for around 3&amp;ndash;4 months.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/myrrhtonkaoil_600x600.jpg?v=1611632502'),
(212, 'F**KING FABULOUS 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 89, 'Eau de Parfum &nbsp;100ml - Censored Version', ' Version About Fucking Fabulous Fucking Fabulous is a shared / unisex perfume by Tom Ford. The scent was launched in 2017. Fucking Fabulous fragrance notes Almond Bitter Oil, Tonka Resinoid, Orris Accord, Cashmeran, Leather Accord, Clary Sage Oil', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/FFCENSORED_600x600.jpg?v=1611641836'),
(213, 'GUCCI BLOOM - ACQUA DI FIORI by GUCCI', 'GUCCI', 569000, 15, '&lt;span&gt;100ml - Eau de Toilette&lt;/span&gt;', 'Bloom Acqua di Fiori Gucci Bloom Acqua di Fiori is a feminine perfume by Gucci. The scent was launched in 2018 and the fragrance was created by perfumer Alberto Morillas Gucci Bloom Acqua di Fiori fragrance notes Top Notes Blackcurrant, Galbanum Heart Notes Chinese honeysuckle, Jasmine, Tuberose Base notes Sandalwood, Musk', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GUCCI-BLOOM-ACQUA-DI-FIORI-EDT-FOR-WOMEN_600x600.jpg?v=1613001886'),
(214, 'CHANEL NO. 5 L&rsquo;EAU RED EDITION by  CHANEL', 'CHANEL', 629000, 56, '100ml - Eau de Toilette', ' Chanel No 5 Parfum Red Edition by Chanel is a Floral Aldehyde fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Chanel No 5 Parfum Red Edition was launched in 2018. Top notes are Aldehydes and Neroli; middle notes are Jasmine and May Rose; base note is Woody Notes.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/image_c9ec359d-9c2c-4b6c-89fe-1441479e0698_600x600.jpg?v=1633487541'),
(215, 'Narciso Rodriguez for him Bleu Noir Extreme EDT', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 589000, 95, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Experience the refreshing vibrancy of Narciso Rodriguez For Him Bleu Noir Extreme Eau de Toilette, a woody-aromatic fragrance for men. Created for the modern man, Narciso Rodriguez&amp;rsquo; fragrance reimagines freshness. Upon the first spritz, the Eau de Toilette welcomes a crisp citrus top note that is created by green mandarin and basil. A heart note of musk creates a deeper, more sensual tone before the base note of blue cedar, black ebony and cistus leave a woody and masculine final statement. Reinventing the original Narciso Rodriguez For Him Bleu Noir, this fragrance focuses on creating an aromatic freshness as opposed to timeless elegance, which Narciso Rodriguez represents in a sturdy bottle that blends from frosted to transparent glass. The Bleu Noir Extreme aroma merges a sense of mystery with a deep intensity, creating a fragrance that is subtle yet seductive.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NARCISOBLEUNOIR_600x600.jpg?v=1614946867'),
(216, 'UN JARDIN SUR LE TOIT by HERMES', 'HERMES', 599000, 36, '100ml Eau de Toilette', ' Un Jardin Sur Le Toit by Herm&amp;egrave;s is a Aromatic Fruity fragrance for women and men. Un Jardin Sur Le Toit was launched in 2011. The nose behind this fragrance is Jean-Claude Ellena. Un Jardin Sur Le Toit refers to the especially luxurious garden located on the Hermes&amp;rsquo; headquarters building roof at 24 Rue Faubourg Saint-Honore in Paris. The garden is full of aromatic herbs, flowers, and fruits whose flavors vary as they pass through the metamorphosis induced by the seasons. Its fresh and sweet-smelling atmosphere is captured by apple, pear, rose, green grass, basil, magnolia, and compost notes.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/UN_JARDIN_SUR_LE_TOIT_1_600x600.jpg?v=1565110943'),
(217, 'Guerlain Shalimar - Eau De Parfum', 'GUERLAIN', 719000, 73, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Guerlain Shalimar Eau De Parfum is a classic oriental fragrance for women. A voluptuous, sensual and embracing fragrance.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Top notes: Bergamot, Lemon&amp;nbsp; Heart notes: Jasmine, Rose, Rose (May Rose or Rose de Mai)&amp;nbsp; Base notes: Iris (Orris), Incense, Opopanax, Tonka bean, Vanilla&amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/guerlainshalimar_600x600.jpg?v=1614948532'),
(218, 'TOBACCO OUD 100ML by TOM FORD', 'TOM FORD', 1190000, 61, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' A private blend, Tobacco Oud explores the secret history of an addictive Arabic passion for crafting fragrances from precious oud wood resin and the smoke of aromatic tobacco. The fragrance intertwines mesmerizing oud with an idealized Arabic tobacco accord inspired by &amp;amp;quot;dokha,&amp;amp;quot; a blend of herbs, flowers and spice-laden tobacco.&amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TOBACCOOUD100ML_600x600.jpg?v=1614948902'),
(219, 'JOY by DIOR', 'DIOR', 579000, 61, '100ml Eau de Parfum', ' Joy by Dior by Christian Dior is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Joy by Dior was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Francois Demachy. Top notes are Bergamot and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Jasmine, Grasse Rose, Peach and Cassis; base notes are White Musk, Sandalwood, Cedar, Patchouli and Benzoin.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/Christian-Dior-Joy_600x600.jpg?v=1566307805'),
(220, 'Bottega Veneta Illusione For Him Eau de Toilette', 'BOTTEGA VENETA', 629000, 75, '90ML Eau de Toilette', ' Bottega Veneta llusione the new aftershave fragrance for him. A suspended moment between dream and reality. The scent is a masculine woody, citrus, aromatic fragrance, combining sparkling colours of Italian citrus with lemon and bitter orange essences. A fresh and aromatic element is added with fir basalm and white cedarwood, with powerful notes of vetiver and sensual tonka been completing the accomplished composition. This light and hazy shaded bottle combines square-shaped architectural lines with a beautiful organic shape in the bottle base reminiscent of a drop of water. A timeless and sensual design.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BOTTEGAFORHIM_600x600.png?v=1614949934'),
(221, 'Gucci The Alchemist\'s Garden: The Virgin Violet', 'GUCCI', 1090000, 45, '100ML Eau de Parfum', 'Alessandro Michele carefully studied the naturally occurring essence of flowers to create each Eau de Parfum in Gucci\'s latest \'The Alchemist\'s Garden\' collection. The designer compares \'The Virgin Violet\' to the elegance of a swan, translated through a blend of Musk, Violet Leaves, and Iris Petals. It\'s housed in a lacquered glass bottle inspired by containers found in a vintage apothecary.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GUCCITHEVIRGINVIOLET_600x600.jpg?v=1614950510'),
(222, 'The Favourite by Penhaligon\'s', 'PENHALIGON&rsquo;S', 1190000, 92, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' The Favourite by Penhaligon&amp;amp;#39;s&amp;nbsp;is a new floral musk fragrance for women. Inspired by the Sarah Churchill, Duchess of Marlborough and the subject of the movie The Favourite, this powdery floral scent includes notes of mandarin, bergamot, and violet leaves blending into a heart of jasmine sambac, mimosa, and orris, with a dry down of ambroxan, musk, and creamy Indian sandalwood. The classic Penhaligon&amp;amp;#39;s perfume bottle features a pale pink hue, red label, golden accents, and is adorned with a pink velvet bow. Launched in 2020, this &amp;amp;quot;smoke and mirrors...iris and musk&amp;amp;quot; feminine fragrance is available in an eau de parfum spray.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/PENHALIGONSTHEFAVORITE_600x600.jpg?v=1614951509'),
(223, 'COCO MADEMOISELLE INTENSE by CHANEL', 'CHANEL', 0, 99, 'Dapatkan promosi dan berita tebaru dari kami.', 'he Coco Mademoiselle personality emerges to forge a powerful, deep, addictive fragrance that is irresistible in every way. Fragrance Notes:&amp;nbsp;An extreme, luminous and deep concentration of Patchouli infuses Coco Mademoiselle Eau De Parfum Intense with a voluptuous dimension. The warm, soft and feminine Amber accord &amp;mdash; an intoxicating blend of Tonka Bean and Vanilla from Madagascar &amp;mdash; wraps the scent in sensuality.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/MADEMOISELLEINTENSE_600x600.jpg?v=1614951949'),
(224, 'BYREDO Night Veil Sellier Extrait de Parfum', 'BYREDO', 1290000, 9, '100ML Extrait de Parfum', ' From a new series of Night Veils - fragrances based around flowers and leather that use raw materials chosen with meticulous care - Byredo presents its Sellier extrait de parfum. Distinguished, sombre, smoky, it is a truly unbridled concentration of leather. The olfactory surprise explodes from the very first second, teleporting you to a vintage smoking room with precious tobacco leaves, antique books and age-worn leather club chairs. Base notes: Birch tree, Oak moss Middle notes: Leather accord, Tobacco leaves Top notes: Cashmeran, Black tea', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOSELLIER_600x600.jpg?v=1614953492'),
(225, 'BYREDO Night Veils Reine de Nuit Extrait de Parfum', 'BYREDO', 1290000, 8, '100ML Extrait de Parfum', ' Distilled into a pure essence, each Night Veils fragrance taps noble raw materials chosen with meticulous care. With its high concentration, this new trio reinvents a new perfume ritual. Reine de Nuit is a testament to how empowering a rich floral perfume can be in the twilight hours. It revives the rich tradition of oriental perfumes and celebrates the intrinsic seductiveness of the rose. Reine de Nuit has a sensual and spellbinding scent.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/c6f5c77b-18fd-4b4f-a087-decb8399e066_600x600.jpg?v=1614953931'),
(226, 'Giorgio Armani My Way EDP 50ML', 'GIORGIO ARMANI', 519000, 37, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Giorgio Armani My Way EDP is an absolutely wonderful feminine fragrance that takes you on probably the most important journey of your life. Namely, to find yourself and your own path through all your experiences and acquaintances. This fragrance has a sensational and uplifting effect on both body and mind, and inspires you to get to know your best sides through nature and other people, so that they can radiate. A timeless scent that with its notes shows that you are an open and curious person who is ready to learn and who is finding his own way in life. The notes in this rich fragrance include tuberose, orange blossom and Indian jasmine, which are the ones that open the fragrance and embrace the body in a wonderful way. Then the bergamot, the white musk, the sweet vanilla and the warm cedar come into their own. They are the ones that collect the scent, and make it more deep and harmonious, and give the final tingle that pushes you out on your journey.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ARMANIMYWAY50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1614954435'),
(227, 'Giorgio Armani My Way EDP 90ML', 'GIORGIO ARMANI', 729000, 15, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Giorgio Armani My Way EDP is an absolutely wonderful feminine fragrance that takes you on probably the most important journey of your life. Namely, to find yourself and your own path through all your experiences and acquaintances. This fragrance has a sensational and uplifting effect on both body and mind, and inspires you to get to know your best sides through nature and other people, so that they can radiate. A timeless scent that with its notes shows that you are an open and curious person who is ready to learn and who is finding his own way in life. The notes in this rich fragrance include tuberose, orange blossom and Indian jasmine, which are the ones that open the fragrance and embrace the body in a wonderful way. Then the bergamot, the white musk, the sweet vanilla and the warm cedar come into their own. They are the ones that collect the scent, and make it more deep and harmonious, and give the final tingle that pushes you out on your journey.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ARMANIMYWAY90ML_600x600.jpg?v=1614954574'),
