(229, 'Marc Jacobs Decadence Eau de Parfum Spray', 'MARC JACOBS', 669000, 82, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Glamourously luxurious. Impulsively indulgent.Marc Jacobs Decadence is an invitation to indulge. It makes a statement with bold styling, luxurious craftsmanship and a revolutionary bottle design inspired by one of Marc?s iconic handbags. Decadence is a indulgent sensual woody scent. The fragrance captivates with a sultry top of succulent italian plum, golden saffron and velvety iris. The heart is a bouquet of rich bulgarian rose that mingles with lush orris and creamy nuances of jasmine sambac. Sexy liquid amber, heady vetiver and warm papyrus woods dry down to a signature of sophisticated indulgence.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/image_b662e6b3-3726-4068-9586-9ba96f48305e_600x600.jpg?v=1623847471'),
(230, 'BYREDO Rose Of No Man\'s Land 100ML', 'BYREDO', 1190000, 61, '100ML Unisex Eau de Parfum', ' Rose of No Man&amp;amp;#39;s Land is the nickname given by soldiers to the nurses who saved thousands of lives during WWI. The scent is tribute to selflessness and compassion. Top: Pink Pepper, Turkish Rose Petals Heart: Raspberry Blossom, Turkish Rose Absolute Base: Papyrus, White Amber', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOROSENOMANLAND_600x600.jpg?v=1614991634'),
(231, 'Bvlgari Rose Goldea', 'BVLGARI', 579000, 79, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Rose Goldea by Bvlgari is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. Rose Goldea was launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Alberto Morillas. Top notes are Rose, Musk, Pomegranate and Bergamot; middle notes are Damask Rose, Peony, Jasmine and Peach; base notes are Musk, Sandalwood, Olibanum and Vanilla.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GOLDEA2016_600x600.jpg?v=1614992040'),
(232, 'Bvlgari Rose Goldea Jacky Tsai Edition', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 29, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Rose Goldea Jacky Tsai Edition by Bvlgari is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Rose Goldea Jacky Tsai Edition was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Alberto Morillas. Top notes are Rose, Pomegranate, Musk and Bergamot; middle notes are Damask Rose, Peony, Jasmine and Peach; base notes are Musk, Vanilla, Sandalwood and Olibanum.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GOLDEA2018_600x600.jpg?v=1614992302'),
(233, 'BYREDO Mojave Ghost 100ML', 'BYREDO', 1190000, 29, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' In the xeric wilderness of the Mojave desert, trees and vegetation more ancient than many civilizations defy conditions that prey on human vulnerability. The ghost flower is a rare species that dares to blossom above this baked, hard ground. Despite its arid surroundings and inability to produce nectar, the ghost flower, or mohavea confertiflora, maintains its perfect, majestic beauty and thrives year after year. In an astonishing feat of ingenuity, the flower uses mimicry to attract the pollinators of a neighboring plant species by developing markings that resemble those of a female bee genus attracted to its subject and duping the male bee into following suit. This moving human-like behavior and captivating tale of survival lies in the foundation that inspired Mojave Ghost, an homage to this most bewitching flower. Style: Woody, aromatic. Notes: - Top: ambrette, Jamaican nesberry. - Middle: violet, sandalwood, magnolia. - Base: chantilly musk, crisp amber, cedarwood.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOMOJAVE_600x600.jpg?v=1614993685'),
(234, 'BYREDO BLANCHE 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 11, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Stockholm-based fragrance house Byredo boasts a bespoke selection of innovative fragrances that refresh traditional olfactory scents, and this Blanche Eau de Parfum one is of no exception. Testament to the brand&amp;amp;#39;s perfumery capabilities and inspired by the naive innocence of the colour white, this scent bestows the appreciation for natural beauty with pure and simple white rose, pink pepper, blonde woods and&amp;nbsp;musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOBLANCHE50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1614993940'),
(235, 'BYREDO Gypsy Water 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 67, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Byredo&amp;amp;#39;s Gypsy Water Eau de Parfum expresses a carefree spirit with down-to-earth nature elements. Recalling the fresh flowing waters and soil of riverbeds and deep forests, this fragrance is the glamorisation of Romany lifestyle in a single phial. Marinated with incense, pine needles and orris over a bed of amber and sandalwood, this velvety concoction is lightened with lemon and pepper for an unlikely aquatic&amp;nbsp;touch.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOGYPSYWATER_600x600.jpg?v=1614994541'),
(236, 'BYREDO SUPER CEDAR 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 28, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Levelled with a silk musk and Haitian vetiver dry down, BYREDO&amp;amp;#39;s newest fragrance, the Super Cedar Eau de Parfum is a new take on woody scents. Evoking simpler times with a sense of nostalgia, this rose petal-infused scent brings to mind freshly shaven pencils. Down-to-earth, it warmly embraces a classic scent with overtly modern&amp;nbsp;attributes. Top notes: Rose petals Heart notes: Virginian cedarwood Base notes: Silk musk and Haitian vetiver', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/SUPERCEDAR_600x600.jpg?v=1614994826'),
(237, 'BYREDO Mojave Ghost 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 11, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' In the xeric wilderness of the Mojave desert, trees and vegetation more ancient than many civilizations defy conditions that prey on human vulnerability. The ghost flower is a rare species that dares to blossom above this baked, hard ground. Despite its arid surroundings and inability to produce nectar, the ghost flower, or mohavea confertiflora, maintains its perfect, majestic beauty and thrives year after year. In an astonishing feat of ingenuity, the flower uses mimicry to attract the pollinators of a neighboring plant species by developing markings that resemble those of a female bee genus attracted to its subject and duping the male bee into following suit. This moving human-like behavior and captivating tale of survival lies in the foundation that inspired Mojave Ghost, an homage to this most bewitching flower. Style: Woody, aromatic. Notes: - Top: ambrette, Jamaican nesberry. - Middle: violet, sandalwood, magnolia. - Base: chantilly musk, crisp amber, cedarwood.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOMOJAVE_51ce626a-b9bc-40fd-ad17-5899397cbf81_600x600.jpg?v=1614994902'),
(239, 'BYREDO Rose Of No Man\'s Land 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 63, '50ML Unisex Eau de Parfum', ' Rose of No Man&amp;amp;#39;s Land is the nickname given by soldiers to the nurses who saved thousands of lives during WWI. The scent is tribute to selflessness and compassion. Top: Pink Pepper, Turkish Rose Petals Heart: Raspberry Blossom, Turkish Rose Absolute Base: Papyrus, White Amber', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOROSENOMANLAND_e4ec810b-52c1-4783-ae46-4f63d8d50a7c_600x600.jpg?v=1614995243'),
(240, 'BYREDO INFLORESCENCE 50ML', 'BYREDO', 799000, 33, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Byredo moves away from classic floral scents in this Inflorescence Eau de Parfum. Redefining feminine fragrances with the pinnacle of Spring blossoms, this one results in a dandified complex of pink freesia and lily of the valley, sprinkled with rose petals for classic sensuality. Uplifted with an unlikely base of jasmine, it embodies a refreshing change from its precursors with a soft and creamy body of&amp;nbsp;magnolia. Top notes: Rose petals and pink freesia Heart notes: Magnolia and lily of the valley Base notes: Fresh Jasmine', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BYREDOINFLORESCENCE_600x600.jpg?v=1614995514'),
(241, 'Amouage Epic Man (Tester Box)', 'AMOUAGE', 999000, 98, '100ML - Eau de Parfum with TESTER BOX', ' Amouage Epic Man by Amouage is a Oriental Woody fragrance for men. Amouage Epic Man was launched in 2009. The nose behind this fragrance is Randa Hammami. Top notes are Pink Pepper, Olibanum, Nutmeg, Saffron, Cardamom, Caraway, Mace and Myrtle; middle notes are Myrrh and Geranium; base notes are Agarwood (Oud), Incense, Leather, Castoreum, Patchouli, Cedar, Sandalowood, Styrax and Musk. &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/AMOUAGEEPICMAN_600x600.png?v=1614996005'),
(242, 'Amouage Library Collection Opus III (Tester Box)', 'AMOUAGE', 999000, 33, '100ML Eau de Parfum with TESTER BOX', ' The Library Collection Opus III by Amouage is a Oriental Floral fragrance for women and men. The Library Collection Opus III was launched in 2010. The nose behind this fragrance is Karine Vinchon Spehner. Top notes are Mimosa, Nutmeg, Clove, Dyer&amp;rsquo;s Greenweed and Thyme; middle notes are Violet, Ylang-Ylang, Jasmine and African Orange flower; base notes are Benzoin, Vanille, Sandalwood, Guaiac Wood, Musk, Ambrette (Musk Mallow), Papyrus and Virginia Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/AMOUAGEOPUSIII_600x600.jpg?v=1614996551'),
(243, 'Amouage Library Collection Opus VII (Tester Box)', 'AMOUAGE', 999000, 96, '100ML Eau de Parfum with TESTER BOX', ' The Library Collection Opus VII by Amouage is an Aromatic Green fragrance for women and men. The Library Collection Opus VII was launched in 2013. The Library Collection Opus VII was created by Alberto Morillas and Pierre Negrin. The fragrance features galbanum, pink pepper, cardamom, fenugreek, nutmeg, amber, agarwood (oud), patchouli, leather, ambergris, costus, musk, sandalwood, olibanum and cypriol oil or nagarmotha.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/AMOUAGEOPUSVII_600x600.jpg?v=1614996891'),
(244, 'LE LABO ROSE 31', 'LE LABO', 799000, 51, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Rose 31 by Le Labo is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women and men. Rose 31 was launched in 2006. The nose behind this fragrance is Daphne Bugey. Top notes are Rose and Cumin; middle notes are Rose, Vetiver and Cedar; base notes are Musk, Guaiac Wood, Agarwood (Oud), Olibanum and Labdanum.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOROSE31_600x600.jpg?v=1615000144'),
(245, 'LE LABO BERGAMOTE 22', 'LE LABO', 799000, 15, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Contrasting notes of petals and bitter citrus fruits make for lasting all-day freshness. Combining the delicate character of floral petit grain with bitter grapefruit, these contrasting notes meet to give Le Labo&amp;amp;#39;s Bergamote 22 Eau de Parfum its unique identity. Initially named &amp;amp;#39;Fire Cologne&amp;amp;#39;, the vegan and cruelty-free fragrance is finished with sweet remnants of amber, musk and vetiver for a dazzling and long-lasting aroma.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOBERGAMOTE22_600x600.jpg?v=1615000400'),
(246, 'LE LABO THE NOIR 29', 'LE LABO', 799000, 55, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Le Labo&amp;amp;#39;s &amp;amp;#39;Th&amp;eacute; Noir 29&amp;amp;#39; eau de parfum combines light notes of Bergamot, Fig and Bay Leaves with heady Cedar Wood, Veitver and Musk. It has a heart of Black Tea Leaves that recall the dry, leafy aroma of Tobacco and Hay. This particular scent in the label&amp;amp;#39;s vast collection is formulated in collaboration with master perfumer Frank Voelkl.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOTHENOIR_600x600.jpg?v=1615000732'),
(247, 'LE LABO IRIS 39', 'LE LABO', 799000, 14, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Iris is one of the most precious essences in the world. It&amp;amp;#39;s the origin of the creamy and woodsy nobility of this exclusive fragrance. The best of the Patchoulis then waft in, bringing with them sensual depth. The perfume is reinforced by a musky base, our very own secret. The result is remarkable elegance.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LELABOIRIS39_600x600.jpg?v=1615001056'),
(250, 'Jour D\'Herm&egrave;s Absolu EDP', 'HERMES', 619000, 40, '85ML Eau de Parfum', ' A new Jour is revealed, zenithal, paradoxical. Gardenia, a bouquet of flowers within a flower bringing together aromas of rose, tuberose and jasmine.Olfactory emotion: Fresh, DelicateMain raw materials: Sweet pea, Gardenia', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/JOURD_HERMES_600x600.jpg?v=1615002595'),
(251, 'DIPTYQUE Impossible Bouquet Eau Moheli', 'DIPTYQUE', 629000, 15, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Impossible Bouquet Eau Moheli by Diptyque is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Impossible Bouquet Eau Moheli was launched in 2020. Top notes are Ginger and Pink Pepper; middle notes are Floral Notes, Ylang-Ylang and Incense; base notes are Benzoin, Vetiver and Patchouli.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUEMOHELI_600x600.jpg?v=1615003293'),
(252, 'DIPTYQUE Impossible Bouquet Eau Des Sens', 'DIPTYQUE', 629000, 21, '100ML Eau de Toilette&lt;br&gt;', 'ossible Bouquet Eau des Sens by Diptyque is a Citrus Aromatic fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Impossible Bouquet Eau des Sens was launched in 2020. Top notes are Orange Blossom and Bitter Orange; middle note is Juniper Berries; base notes are Patchouli and Angelica. &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUEDESSENS_600x600.jpg?v=1615003985'),
(253, 'DIPTYQUE Impossible Bouquet Eau Rose', 'DIPTYQUE', 629000, 76, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Impossible Bouquet Eau Rose by Diptyque is a Floral Fruity fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Impossible Bouquet Eau Rose was launched in 2020. Top notes are Litchi, Black Currant and Bergamot; middle notes are Rose, Geranium and Jasmine; base notes are Honey, Musk and Virginian Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUEROSE_600x600.jpg?v=1615004249'),
(255, 'DIPTYQUE Impossible Bouquet Do Son', 'DIPTYQUE', 629000, 27, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Impossible Bouquet Do Son by Diptyque is a Floral fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Impossible Bouquet Do Son was launched in 2020. Top notes are Orange Blossom, Rose and iris; middle notes are Tuberose and Pink Pepper; base notes are Benzoin and Musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUEDOSON_600x600.jpg?v=1615004819'),
(256, 'DIPTYQUE Impossible Bouquet Olene', 'DIPTYQUE', 629000, 70, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Impossible Bouquet Olene by Diptyque is a Floral fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Impossible Bouquet Olene was launched in 2020. Top notes are Narcissus and Honeysuckle; middle notes are Jasmine and Wisteria; base notes are White Flowers and Green Notes.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUEOLENE_600x600.jpg?v=1615005307'),
(257, 'Maison Margiela REPLICA Lazy Sunday Morning Lunar New Year Limited Edition', 'MAISON MARGIELA', 819000, 50, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' Maison Margiela&amp;amp;#39;s fragrance Lazy Sunday Morning, from the Replica line (abbreviated from &amp;amp;quot;Reproduction of Familiar Scents and Moments of Varying Locations and Periods&amp;amp;quot;) that captures memories and moments hidden in our memories, was created by&amp;nbsp;Louise Turner in 2013 with the scent of soft skin and clean cotton sheets in mind. The location for inspiration is Florence, and the period is 2003. To celebrate the Chinese New Year 2021 (the lunar new year that begins on February 12), a special limited edition of this fragrance in a red bottle is launched. The clean floral composition blends notes of iris, lily of the valley and white musk for an atmosphere of fresh cotton sheets, morning air, and rays of sun, as well as the atmosphere of weekend laziness in bed. Top notes: aldehydes, pear, lily of the valleyHeart: rose absolute, iris, orange blossomBase: white musk, ambrette seeds, Indonesian patchouli', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/REPLICALAZYSUNDAYMORNING_600x600.jpg?v=1615005845'),
(258, 'Gucci M&eacute;moire d\'une Odeur', 'GUCCI', 579000, 54, '100ml Eau de Parfum', ' M&amp;eacute;moire d&amp;rsquo;une Odeur by Gucci is a fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. M&amp;eacute;moire d&amp;rsquo;une Odeurwas launched in 2019. The nose behind this fragrance is Alberto Morillas. Top notes are Chamomile and Bitter Almond; middle notes are Musk, Indian Jasmine and Jasmine; base notes are Sandalwood, Cedar and Vanilla.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/gucci_gucci-memoire-d-une-odeur-unisex-edp--100ml-_full01_600x600.jpg?v=1615007266');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `name`, `brand`, `price`, `stock`, `type`, `description`, `image_source`) VALUES
(259, 'Anna Sui Fantasia 30ML', 'ANNA SUI', 379000, 84, '30ML Eau de Toilette', ' The new Eau de Toilette uses unicorn as the protagonist, vowing to arouse childhood dreams and aspirations, even as a grown up, still does not forget the desire for life and the potential of a passionate passion. Even already has a sweet and happy life, still keeps the passion for life, with a rebellious spirit. The perfume smells a little spicy, very well to reflect how Fantasia&amp;rsquo;s Muse is &amp;ndash; a rebellious beauty, has a complex contradictive character, always has her own ideas, is a set of sweetness and excitement in a perfect and unique girl. Ingredients and efficacy:Top Notes: Citrus, pink pepper.Middle Notes: Floral elements, raspberry, nuts candies.Base Notes: Himalayan cedar, cypress.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ANNASUIFANTASIA_600x600.jpg?v=1615009036'),
(260, 'Fantasia Mermaid Anna Sui 30ML', 'ANNA SUI', 399000, 18, '30ML Eau de Toilette', ' Fantasia Mermaid by Anna Sui is a Floral Fruity Gourmand fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Fantasia Mermaid was launched in 2019. The nose behind this fragrance is Christian Provenzano. Top notes are Blood Orange, Cardamom and Mandarin Orange; middle notes are Litchi, Peony and Jasmine; base notes are Honey, White Wood and Vanilla.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/FANTASIAMERMAID_600x600.jpg?v=1615009406'),
(261, 'MFK &Agrave; la Rose Travel spray case Gold edition 5 x 0.37 fl.oz. Eau de parfum refills', 'MAISON FRANCIS KURKDJIAN', 1090000, 56, '5 x 0.37 fl.oz. Eau de parfum refills', ' A bouquet of roses from Grasse and Bulgaria that you can carry in your handbag or suitcase. &amp;Agrave; la rose is a tribute to free and radiant femininity. Presented in a travel set containing five 0.37 fl.oz. refills and a Gold Edition Globe Trotter travel spray case, &amp;Agrave; la rose is a declaration of love translated into a fragrance.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ALAROSESET5_600x600.jpg?v=1615011472'),
(262, 'MON PARIS EDP 50ML by YVES SAINT LAURENT', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 419000, 64, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Capturing the spirit of an intense love affair, YSL introduces Mon Paris perfume - a new expression of love today, inspired by the city of lovers, Paris. Mon Paris is a fragrance which urges you to seize the moment; transcend the present; and prepare to fall head over heels into the arms of a passionate love. A subversive reinvention of the traditional chypre, the new floral perfume turns the traditional model upside down, by introducing a brave, bold narcotic white chypre fit for love today.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/MONPARISEDP50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1615180689'),
(263, 'Yves Saint Lauren Mon Paris Eau De Parfum 30ml Fireworks Collector Edition', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 359000, 88, '30ML Eau de Parfum', ' Mon Paris Dazzling Lights Collector by Yves Saint Laurent is a chypre fruity fragrance. Top notes: strawberry, raspberry, pear, bergamot, calone, orange, mandarin orange. Middle notes: Datura, peony, orange blossom, jasmine sambac, Chinese jasmine. Base notes: patchouli, musk, ambroxan, cedar, moss, vanilla, Indonesian patchouli leaf.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/monpariscollector30ml_600x600.jpg?v=1615199140'),
(264, 'NARCISO RODRIGUEZ For Her EDT 75ml (Generous Spray)', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 549000, 14, '75ML Eau de Toilette Generous Spray', ' Enjoy the graciousness that is Narciso Rodriguez&amp;amp;#39;s limited edition Generous Spray. An enveloping mist of our best-selling fragrances. An elegant, sensual, mysterious and delicate fragrance. Three notes enhance the heart of musk: floral, amber and woody notes. Fragrance family: musky, floral, chypre. Top Notes: osmanthus blossom Heart Notes: heart of musc Base Notes: patchouli, amberlyn', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NARCISOFORHEREDTGENEROUS_600x600.jpg?v=1615181947'),
(265, 'Narciso Rodriguez For Her EDP 50ML', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 479000, 73, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Narciso for Her perfume is created for very sensitive, delicate and free modern women. The aroma is filled with notes of musk and enhanced with floral, woody and amber notes, which are combined to create the effect of sexuality, charm and mystery. Aroma type: musky, floral. Top notes: orange, coriander, Egyptian musk. Heart notes: bergamot, osmanthus, vanilla. Base notes: vetiver, flower honey, amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NARCISOFORHEREDP_600x600.jpg?v=1615182292'),
(266, 'Narciso Rodriguez Generous Spray EDP Poudr&eacute;e, 75ml', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 549000, 85, '75ML Eau de Parfum Generous Spray', ' Enjoy the graciousness that is Narciso Rodriguez&amp;amp;#39;s limited edition Generous Spray. An enveloping mist of our best-selling fragrances. The mystery of attraction captured in a fragrance. The rendez-vous between velvety jamine, sensual wood and powdery musc. Fragrance family: Powdery, musky, floral, woody Top Notes: white jasmine petals &amp;amp;amp;amp; Bulgarian rose Heart Notes: powdery heart of musc Base Notes: white and black cedars, vetiver.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/93880872-f952-4403-bba7-1896d7520731_600x600.jpg?v=1615182922'),
(267, 'Narciso Rodriguez Generous Spray Rouge EDP 75ML', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 549000, 6, '57ML Eau de Parfum Generous Spray', ' Enjoy the graciousness that is Narciso Rodriguez&amp;amp;#39;s limited edition Generous Spray. An enveloping mist of our best-selling fragrances. A fragrance that explores the fine art of temptation further. &amp;nbsp; The signature heart of musc is animated by an exquisite floral bouquet of bulgarian rose, iris and vivid amber woody notes. &amp;nbsp; Fragrance family: Ambery, floral, musky, woody. Top Notes: bulgarian rose and iris Heart Notes: heart of musc Base Notes: Tonka, Vetiver, Black cedar / White cedar &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NARCISOROUGE_600x600.png?v=1615183194'),
(268, 'Narciso Rodriguez Generous Spray Fleur Musc for Her EDP 75ML', 'Narciso Rodriguez', 549000, 38, '75ML Eau de Parfum Generous Spray', ' Enjoy the graciousness that is Narciso Rodriguez&amp;amp;#39;s limited edition Generous Spray. An enveloping mist of our best-selling fragrances. The for her signature heart of musc is surrounded by roses, spices, and amber wood, to create a sparkling fragrance. Fragrance family: Spicy, musky, floral, chypre. Top Notes: Bouquet of roses and pink Peppercorns Heart Notes: Heart of Musc Base Notes: Amber, Patchouli', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NARCISOFORHERGENEROUS75ML_600x600.jpg?v=1615183524'),
(269, 'Amouage Interlude Man EDP Spray (Tester Box)', 'AMOUAGE', 999000, 40, '100ML Eau de Parfum TESTER BOX', ' Amouage Interlude Man is inspired by chaos and disorder. This spicy and woody fragrance opens with zesty bergamot, oregano and pimento berry oil, perpetuating intervals of conflict which are countered by aromatic notes of amber, frankincense, opoponax, cistus and myrrh. Eternal notes of leather, agarwood smoke, patchouli and sandalwood in the base add lasting layers of depth and texture. Made in Oman.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/AMOUAGEINTERLUDE_600x600.jpg?v=1615184222'),
(271, 'MISS DIOR EAU DE PARFUM 100ML', 'DIOR', 629000, 73, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' The new Miss Dior Eau de Parfum reveals the femininity of a sensual floral. Its heart is a floral declaration that combines the beauty of Grasse rose with the boldness of Damascus rose, both wrapped in a ribbon of fresh notes of Calabrian bergamot. This handcrafted creation is woven with rosewood from French Guiana and pink pepper from Reunion Island for heightened character. A Miss Dior that will leave you&amp;nbsp;lovestruck.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/MISSDIOREDP_600x600.jpg?v=1626917942'),
(272, 'Versace Bright Crystal Eau De Toilette Spray 30ML', 'VERSACE', 349000, 5, '30ML Eau de Toilette', ' Sheer sensuality, crystal transparency, and luminous brightness: Versace introduces Bright Crystal, a precious jewel of rare beauty characterized by a fresh, vibrant, flowery scent. The bottle is extraordinary: rich glass, lines purposely essential, the transparency of which enhances the pinky delicacy of the fragrance. The very elegant crystal cap, faceted and bright like a diamond, seals a bouquet of extreme pureness. Bright Crystal is bursting with juicy notes of pomegranate, pretty magnolia, peony and lotus flowers with amber and musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/VERSACEBRIGHT30ML_600x600.jpg?v=1626918440'),
(273, 'Bvlgari Man Glacial Essence Eau de Parfum', 'BVLGARI', 629000, 33, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' BVLGARI MAN GLACIAL ESSENCE enriches the Bvlgari Man collection dedicated to the power of natural elements. After fire and wood, Bvlgari Man explores air. BVLGARI MAN GLACIAL ESSENCE captures the unbridled magnitude of the frozen mountains and the unstoppable masculinity of a man on a constant quest for greatness. Top notes are Juniper Berries, Ginger and Geranium; middle notes are Sandalwood, Artemisia and Orris Root; base notes are Clearwood, Musk and Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLGARIMENGLACIAL_600x600.jpg?v=1626919444'),
(274, 'CHANCE Eau Fraiche by Chanel', 'CHANEL', 619000, 18, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' A floral-sparkling fragrance in a round bottle. A surge of energy that sweeps you into a whirlwind of happiness and fantasy. An olfactory encounter with chance. A floral-sparkling fragrance that intertwines the zesty freshness of Citron, the softness of Jasmine and the vibrant presence of Teak Wood. A whirlwind of energy and vitality.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/CHANCEFRAICHE_600x600.jpg?v=1626920264'),
(275, 'Bvlgari BLV Pour Homme Eau De Toilette Spray', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 58, '100ML Eau de Toilette&nbsp;', 'mp;nbsp; From icy cold to luxuriously warm, BLV Pour Homme is a fresh, woody and spicy Eau de Toilette. Built around the same unconventional ingredient as BLV-ginger-and combined with tobacco flower, BLV Pour Homme discloses an irresistible power of seduction.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BLV-Pour-homme_600x600.jpg?v=1626920639'),
(276, 'Bvlgari Eau Parfumee Au The Bleu Eau de Cologne - Unisex', 'BVLGARI', 519000, 72, '75ML Eau Perfumee Eau de Cologne', ' Eau Parfumee au The Bleu by Bvlgari is a Aromatic fragrance for women and men. Eau Parfumee au The Bleu was launched in 2015. The nose behind this fragrance is Daniela (Roche) Andrier. Top notes are Lavender and Shiso; middle notes are Tea and Violet; base notes are iris and Musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLGARIEAUTHEBLEU_600x600.jpg?v=1626921179'),
(277, 'Bvlgari Eau Parfumee au The Noir for Women - Eau de Cologne', 'BVLGARI', 519000, 14, '75ML Eau Parfum&eacute;e Eau de Cologne', 'de Cologne Bvlgari Eau Parfumee Au The Noir Perfume by Bvlgari, Created by French perfumer Jacques Cavallier, the unisex Eau Parfumee Au The Noir (black tea) is an Oriental woody perfume with an elegant black tea aroma and deep tobacco and leather scents. The opening floral notes come from rose while the citrus notes are derived from citrus bergamia, otherwise known as bergamot orange. Magnolia and tea provide the floral and green center notes while the base notes consist of leather, patchouli, and oud, or agarwood, which is a fragrant, expensive wood that is often used to make high quality incense.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLGARIEAUTHENOIR_600x600.jpg?v=1626921656'),
(278, 'Dior Addict Eau Fra&icirc;che 50ML', 'DIOR', 499000, 48, '50ML Eau de Toilette Spray', ' A crisp botanic fragrance with an oriental trail and &amp;amp;#39;second skin&amp;amp;#39; feel. Dior Addict Eau Fraiche radiates a glowing femininity. Top notes of gentle Calabrian Bergamot and the sweet and sour citrus notes of Grapefruit blend into the elegant floral notes of Freesia and Lily of the Valley. Ending on a sensuous woody, white musk base, Dior Addict Eau Fra&amp;icirc;che is a fresh, feminine experience.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIORADDICT50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1626922276'),
(279, 'Dior Addict Eau de Parfum 50ML', 'BVLGARI', 499000, 40, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Dior Addict Eau de Parfum (2014) by Dior is a Amber Floral fragrance for women. Dior Addict Eau de Parfum (2014)was launched in 2014. The nose behind this fragrance is Francois Demachy. Top notes are Mandarin Leaf and Orange Blossom; middle note is Jasmine Sambac; base note is Bourbon Vanilla.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIORADDICTEDP_600x600.jpg?v=1626922618'),
(280, 'Bvlgari Allegra Magnifying Bergamot EDP 40ML', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 78, '40ML Eau de Parfum', ' MAGNIFYING comprises of precious tailor-made ingredients to intensify magnificent Italian emotions. As their name suggests, these essences are highly concentrated, powerful and vibrant, an expression of true exclusivity. The citrus essence bursts with solar energy. To achieve this especially bright distillation, Calabrian bergamot is harvested when it&amp;rsquo;s perfectly ripe. Fresh-picked, the bergamot contains sweet and crisp notes. Distilled to retain the fruit&amp;rsquo;s multi-faceted freshness, MAGNIFYING BERGAMOT exudes the upbeat promise of a gorgeous summer&amp;amp;#39;s day. &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLBERGAMOT_600x600.png?v=1626925414'),
(281, 'Bvlgari Allegra Magnifying Musk EDP 40ML', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 30, '40ML Eau de Parfum', ' MAGNIFYING comprises of precious tailor-made ingredients to intensify magnificent Italian emotions. As their name suggests, these essences are highly concentrated, powerful and vibrant, an expression of true exclusivity. The warm and sultry essence of MAGNIFYING MUSK is inspired by the intimate feel of touch. Crafted with ambrette, the deceptively simple musk reveals a sophisticated radiance. With its notable and expressive luminosity, Magnifying Musk recalls the dazzling joy of an embrace.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLMUSK_600x600.png?v=1626925325'),
(282, 'Bvlgari Allegra Magnifying Patchouli EDP 40ML', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 72, '40ML Eau de Parfum', ' MAGNIFYING comprises of precious tailor-made ingredients to intensify magnificent Italian emotions. As their name suggests, these essences are highly concentrated, powerful and vibrant, an expression of true exclusivity. The elegant essence of MAGNIFYING PATCHOULI enchants with a stark sensuality. Made with patchouli sourced from Indonesia, the opulent distillation is of unprecedented quality, free of any dark, earthy notes by exclusive fractionation. Enriched with woody and chypre facets, Magnifying Patchouli rouses a precious and powerful seduction.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLPATCHOULI_600x600.jpg?v=1626925735'),
(283, 'Bvlgari Allegra Magnifying Rose EDP 40ML', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 13, '40ML Eau de Parfum', ' MAGNIFYING comprises of precious tailor-made ingredients to intensify magnificent Italian emotions. As their name suggests, these essences are highly concentrated, powerful and vibrant, an expression of true exclusivity. The floral essence of MAGNIFYING ROSE entices with a velvety, voluptuous intensity. Unlike a classic, powdery rose, this blend of Bulgarian and Turkish roses boasts a remarkable radiance, thanks to a unique fragmentation of essential oils with an unusual distillation. With a sparkle refined by subtle woody notes, Magnifying Rose delivers a luscious bouquet full of the optimism of love.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLROSE_600x600.png?v=1626925539'),
(284, 'Bvlgari Allegra Magnifying Vanilla EDP 40ML', 'BVLGARI', 599000, 93, '40ML Eau de Parfum', ' MAGNIFYING comprises of precious tailor-made ingredients to intensify magnificent Italian emotions. As their name suggests, these essences are highly concentrated, powerful and vibrant, an expression of true exclusivity. The delicately sweet essence of MAGNIFYING VANILLA tantalises, with vanilla beans imported from Madagascar. To develop the fruit&amp;rsquo;s most complex and nuanced facets, it&amp;rsquo;s dried in the sun. Raw, leathery and sexy notes culminate in an addictive aroma, and Magnifying Vanilla ignites an irresistible attraction.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/BVLVANILLA_600x600.jpg?v=1626925605'),
(285, 'HERMES L\'Ombre des Merveilles Eau de parfum - UNISEX', 'HERMES', 649000, 34, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' The intense radiance of a chiariscuro fragrance, both woody and oriental.The sensuality of tonka bean and incense emphasized by deep notes of black tea.Olfactory emotion: Spicy, DryMain raw materials: Tonka bean, Black tea, Incense', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/HERMESL_OMBRE_600x600.jpg?v=1626926803'),
(286, 'HERMES Eau des Merveilles Eau de toilette', 'HERMES', 629000, 59, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' An enchanting perfume, warm and sparkling.A fragrance composed of smooth, vanilla toned benzoin and ambergris woody notes, a wonderful stroll in the refreshing cool of wild orange trees.Olfactory emotion: Spicy, DryMain raw materials: Elemi, Benzoin, Bitter orange', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/HERMESEAUDEMERVEILLES_600x600.jpg?v=1626927146'),
(287, 'Yves Saint Laurent Libre Collector\'s Edition EDP (Dress Me Wild)', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 659000, 61, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Libre Collector Edition is a new and limited perfume by Yves Saint Laurent&amp;nbsp;in a collector&amp;amp;#39;s bottle for women and was released in 2020 The sexy, cool, and floral &amp;ldquo;dress me wild&amp;rdquo; edition opens with notes of lavender, mandarin, and neroli in the opening notes; in the heart are orange and jasmine flowers, while the base combines vanilla, tonka, and white musk. &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LIBRELEOPARD_600x600.jpg?v=1626927875'),
(288, 'Black Opium Shine On Yves Saint Laurent - Limited Edition', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 659000, 67, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Black Opium Shine On by Yves Saint Laurent is a Amber Vanilla fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Black Opium Shine On was launched in 2019. Black Opium Shine On was created by Nathalie Lorson, Marie Salamagne, Olivier Cresp and Honorine Blanc. Top notes are Pink Pepper, Orange Blossom and Pear; middle notes are Coffee, Jasmine, Almond and Licorice; base notes are Vanilla, Patchouli, Cashmere Wood and Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/OPIUMSHINEONEDP_600x600.jpg?v=1626929190'),
(289, 'Black Opium EDP Holiday Collector Bottle Edition', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 659000, 16, '90ML - Eau de Parfum', ' To celebrate the festive season, YSL Beauty offers a wild twist on a holiday classic: Black Opium, now dressed in NEW glittering limited edition pattern. The NEW Black Opium collector houses the much-loved Black Opium original Eau de Parfum. A captivating floral gourmand scent, twisted with an overdose of black coffee, for a shot of adrenaline. Energy, sensuality, coupled with that unique YSL edge.The signature black coffee accord is paired with creamy vanilla, enriched by the softness of white flowers and orange blossom, against a base of patchouli and comforting white musk, for a women&amp;rsquo;s fragrance that bewitches with its trail. Crafted by Marie Salamagne, Nathalie Lorson, Olivier Cresp and Honorine Blanc. &amp;bull; Top notes: pear accord, mandarin essence&amp;bull; Heart notes: vanilla, orange blossom, white flowers&amp;bull; Base notes: black coffee accord, cedarwood essence, white musk, patchouli', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/OPIUMRED_600x600.jpg?v=1626929753'),
(290, 'Nomade by CHLOE 75ml EDP', 'CHLOE', 619000, 16, '75ML Eau de Parfum', ' Chlo&amp;eacute; Nomade Eau de Parfum encapsulates the spirit of a woman open to the beauty of the World, who flourishes through her experiences and encounters. A perfume with an intense character of oak moss, shrouded in the sweetness of cherry plum and the freshness of freesia.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/NOMADECHLOE_600x600.jpg?v=1626930430'),
(291, 'Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet 50ML', 'DIOR', 499000, 31, '50ML Eau de Toilette', ' Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette is a delicate and playful scent that truly feels like spring in a bottle and that embodies the Miss Dior spirit perfectly. As its antecedents, the Dior Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet Eau de Toilette has a sophisticated flask that immediately reminds us of the couture luxurious spirit. Introduce this enchanting scent as your daily perfume, and complement its use with other products from the same range in order to enhance its fragrance trail. Top notes: sicilian mandarin, calabrian bergamot; Heart notes: pink peony, damask rose, apricot and peach; Base notes: white musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/MISSDIOR50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1626943135'),
(292, 'TERRE D\'HERMES EDT 50 ML by HERMES', 'HERMES', 499000, 82, '50ML - Eau de Toilette', 'e d&amp;amp;#39;Hermes by Herm&amp;egrave;s is a Woody Spicy fragrance for men. Terre d&amp;amp;#39;Hermes was launched in 2006. The nose behind this fragrance is Jean-Claude Ellena. Top notes are Orange and Grapefruit; middle notes are Pepper and Pelargonium; base notes are Vetiver, Cedar, Patchouli and Benzoin. This perfume is the winner of award FiFi Award Fragrance Of The Year Men`s Luxe 2007.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TERRE50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1626943595'),
(293, 'Gucci Bloom Eau de Parfum 50ml', 'GUCCI', 429000, 48, '50ML Eau de Parfum', ' Gucci Bloom Eau de Parfum is a scent that celebrates authenticity, vitality as well as the diversity of women &amp;mdash; flourishing in a natural, expressive and individual way. Blended by master perfumer Alberto Morillas under the direction of the House&amp;rsquo;s Creative Director, Gucci Bloom is created to unfold like its name, capturing the rich scent of a thriving garden filled with an abundance of flowers. Tuberose and jasmine coupled with Rangoon Creeper &amp;mdash; a unique flower from South India that is for the first time in perfumery to create a rich fragrance that transports the wearer to an imaginary garden. Top notes: jasmine; Heart notes: tuberose; Base notes: rangoon creeper.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/GUCCIBLOOMEDP50ML_600x600.jpg?v=1626944272'),
(294, 'Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming by DIOR 100ML', 'DIOR', 649000, 55, '100ML Eau de Parfum', ' Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming by Dior is a Floral Fruity fragrance for women. Miss Dior Absolutely Blooming was launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Francois Demachy. Top notes are Raspberry, Black Currant, Pomegranate and Pink Pepper; middle notes are May Rose and Peony; base note is White Musk. &amp;nbsp;', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/MISSDIORABSOLUTELYBLOOMING_600x600.jpg?v=1626946851'),
(295, 'Davidoff Cool Water Eau de Toilette', 'DAVIDOFF', 569000, 30, '125ML Eau de Toilette', ' Davidoff Cool Water Eau de Toilette For Men is an original marine fragrance for men, inspired by the freshness of the ocean. Cool Water is the aromatic essence of masculine vitality, power and seduction. An invigorating scent delivers energy as well as audacity. With refreshing top notes of lavender coupled with peppermint, the perfume opens with vibrant and sparkling intensity. The heart notes of sandalwood, geranium together with oakmoss add body and presence to the fragrance. Deeper notes of musk and amber are the base notes that add more intensity as well as an interesting contrast.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DAVIDOFFEDT_600x600.jpg?v=1627008973'),
(296, 'Mon Paris Eau de Parfum 90ML by YVES SAINT LAURENT', 'YVES SAINT LAURENT', 569000, 1, '90ML Eau de Parfum', ' Capturing the spirit of an intense love affair, YSL introduces Mon Paris perfume - a new expression of love today, inspired by the city of lovers, Paris. Mon Paris is a fragrance which urges you to seize the moment; transcend the present; and prepare to fall head over heels into the arms of a passionate love. A subversive reinvention of the traditional chypre, the new floral perfume turns the traditional model upside down, by introducing a brave, bold narcotic white chypre fit for love today.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/image_e6f20446-4db4-4668-990d-9339ebf110a6_600x600.jpg?v=1628826512'),
(297, 'Red Wood DSQUARED2 For Women', 'DSQUARED2', 549000, 18, 'Eau de Toilette - 100ML', ' Red Wood by DSQUARED2&amp;nbsp;is a Floral Fruity fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Red Wood was launched in 2019. Top notes are Cranberry and Pink Pepper; middle notes are Litchi, Magnolia and Rose; base notes are Cedar, Amberwood and Musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/dsquared2-red-wood-w-edt-100ml_600x600.jpg?v=1634003213'),
(298, 'L\'Eau D\'Issey Pour Homme Issey Miyake', 'ISSEY MIYAKE', 529000, 66, 'Eau de Toilette - 125ML', ' L&amp;amp;#39;Eau d&amp;amp;#39;Issey Pour Homme by Issey Miyake is a Woody Aquatic fragrance for men. L&amp;amp;#39;Eau d&amp;amp;#39;Issey Pour Homme was launched in 1994. The nose behind this fragrance is Jacques Cavallier. Top notes are Yuzu, Lemon, Bergamot, Lemon Verbena, Mandarin Orange, Cypress, Calone, Coriander, Tarragon and Sage; middle notes are Blue Lotus, Nutmeg, Lily-of-the-Valley, Saffron, Ceylon Cinnamon, Bourbon Geranium and Mignonette; base notes are Tahitian Vetiver, Musk, Cedar, Sandalwood, Tobacco and Amber.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ISSEYMIYAKEEDT_600x600.png?v=1634005661'),
(299, 'Acqua di Gi&ograve; Absolu Giorgio Armani', 'GIORGIO ARMANI', 649000, 96, 'Eau de Parfum - 125ML', ' Acqua di Gi&amp;ograve; Absolu by Giorgio Armani is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. Acqua di Gi&amp;ograve; Absolu was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Alberto Morillas. Top notes are Sea Notes, Bergamot, Pear, Grapefruit, Apple and Lemon; middle notes are Lavender, Geranium and Rosemary; base notes are Woody Notes, Tonka Bean, Patchouli, Amberwood and Labdanum.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ARMANIABSOLU125_600x600.jpg?v=1634006830'),
(300, 'Kenzo World EDP by KENZO', 'KENZO', 579000, 71, 'Eau de Parfum - 75 ML', ' Kenzo World by Kenzo is a Floral fragrance for women. Kenzo World was launched in 2016. The nose behind this fragrance is Francis Kurkdjian. Top note is Red Fruits; middle notes are Peony, Floral Notes and Egyptian Jasmine; base note is Ambroxan.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/KENZOWORLDEDP_600x600.jpg?v=1634007376'),
(301, 'Ouverture Xerjoff Velvet Collection', 'XERJOFF', 1190000, 30, 'Eau de Parfum - 100ML', ' Ouverture by Xerjoff is a Amber Floral fragrance for women and men. This is a new fragrance. Ouverture was launched in 2019. The nose behind this fragrance is Chris Maurice. Top notes are Fig Leaf, Orange and Magnolia; middle notes are Indian Jasmine, Bulgarian Rose, Cinnamon and Ylang-Ylang; base notes are Sandalwood, Vanilla, Cashmere Wood, Amber and Incense.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/XERJOFFOUVERTURE_600x600.jpg?v=1634008063'),
(302, 'Metallique Tom Ford', 'TOM FORD', 1090000, 69, 'Eau de parfum - 100ML', ' Metallique by Tom Ford is a Floral Aldehyde fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Metallique was launched in 2019. Top notes are Aldehydes, Pink Pepper and Bergamot; middle notes are Heliotrope, Hawthorn and Lily-of-the-Valley; base notes are Vanilla, Ambrette (Musk Mallow), Peru Balsam and Sandalwood.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TFMETALLIQUE_600x600.jpg?v=1634009175'),
(303, '212 VIP Ros&eacute; Red Carolina Herrera', 'CAROLINA HERRERA', 619000, 61, 'Eau de Parfum - 80ML', ' 212 VIP Ros&amp;eacute; Red by Carolina Herrera is a Floral Fruity fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. 212 VIP Ros&amp;eacute; Red was launched in 2020. Top notes are Liquor, Tomato and Raspberry; middle notes are Tiramisu, Spices and Bulgarian Rose; base notes are Patchouli, Musk and Woody Notes.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/212ROSERED_600x600.jpg?v=1634009769'),
(304, 'Dolce &amp; Gabbana Light Blue EDT for Women', 'DOLCE &amp; GABBANA', 529000, 31, 'Eau de Toilette - 100ML', ' Dolce &amp;amp;amp;amp; Gabbana Light Blue&amp;nbsp;perfume has combination of lively Sicilian citron and effervescent Granny Smith Apples, are softened and ethereally blended with the intensity of freesia, jasmine, earthy musk and amber Dolce &amp;amp;amp;amp; Gabbana Light Blue is a stunning fragrance&amp;nbsp;that&amp;amp;#39;s both overwhelming and irresistible, like the joy of living', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/LIGHTBLUED_G_600x600.jpg?v=1634011011'),
(305, 'Wood for Her DSQUARED2', 'DSQUARED2', 549000, 8, 'Eau de Toilette - 100ML', ' Wood for Her by DSQUARED2&amp;nbsp;is a Floral Woody Musk fragrance for women. This is a new fragrance. Wood for Her was launched in 2018. Top notes are Raspberry Leaf, Mandarin Orange, Magnolia and Lily-of-the-Valley; middle notes are Osmanthus and Jasmine; base notes are White Woods, Ambroxan and Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DSQUARED2WOOD_600x600.jpg?v=1634011591'),
(306, 'Noir Extreme Tom Ford (TESTER BOX)', 'TOM FORD', 899000, 41, 'Eau de Parfum - 100ML (TESTER BOX)', ' Noir Extreme by Tom Ford is a Amber Woody fragrance for men. Noir Extreme was launched in 2015. The nose behind this fragrance is Sonia Constant. Top notes are Cardamom, Nutmeg, Saffron, Mandarin Orange and Neroli; middle notes are Kulfi, Rose, Jasmine, Mastic or Lentisque and Orange Blossom; base notes are Vanilla, Amber, Woody Notes and Sandalwood.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/TOMFORDNOIREXTREME_600x600.jpg?v=1634012115'),
(307, 'Diptyque 34 L\'Eau Du Trente-Quatre', 'DIPTYQUE', 719000, 51, '100ML Eau de Toilette', ' From the 34 Boulevard Satin-Germain collection celebrating diptyque&amp;amp;#39;s 50th anniversary, 34 L&amp;amp;#39;Eau du Trent-Quatre Eau de Toilette captures the scent of the first boutique during spring, when the weather changes and the greenest notes take over the warmer and sensual notes. Style: Green, woody, floral. Notes: grapefruit, bitter orange, fig leaves, galbanum, Egyptian, geranium, tuberose, cinnamon, nutmeg, cedarwood, vetiver, white musk.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/DIPTYQUE34L_EAU_600x600.jpg?v=1635859966'),
(308, 'Good Girl L&eacute;g&egrave;re Carolina Herrera (TESTER BOX)', 'CAROLINA HERRERA', 549000, 92, '80ML Eau de Parfum (Tester Box)', ' Good Girl L&amp;eacute;g&amp;egrave;re by Carolina Herrera is a Amber Floral fragrance for women. Good Girl L&amp;eacute;g&amp;egrave;re was launched in 2018. The nose behind this fragrance is Louise Turner. Top notes are Ylang-Ylang, Mandarin Orange, Lemon and Bergamot; middle notes are Jasmine, Tuberose, Orange Blossom and Bulgarian Rose; base notes are Dulce de leche, Tonka Bean, Praline, Cinnamon, Sandalwood, Cashmirwood, Amber, Musk, Patchouli and Cedar.', '//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0020/6359/7631/products/ScreenShot2021-11-02at20.57.20_600x600.png?v=1635861626');
